Plot:
What Ngamphan, the expert queer of beauty contest, will do when she lacks of anyone to join the contest? Lalabelle, her friend who is the same age as her mom, and Sarinee, the girl friend who would like to have Ngamphan's heart, try to search for anyone who can join this contest. Finally, they get Banjong, the Chinese opera actor, who complies to be a queer to join the contest. Dok Keaw, the queer foe, observes everything. What will be going on? To be continued.
